    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://chicago.craigslist.org/chc/fbh/6046973585.html"></div>
        </div>
Acanto is a popular Michigan Avenue restaurant,  just steps from Millennium Park, serving upscale Italian cuisine. We are in search of a Sous Chef who will assist with the daily operations of the kitchen and provide professional leadership and direction to kitchen personnel. Among other duties, the perfect candidate will ensure that all recipes, food preparations, and presentations meet our restaurant's specifications and unwavering commitment to quality. <br>
<br>
<br>
REQUIREMENTS:<br>
-At least 2 years of Sous Chef experience<br>
-Strong working knowledge of BOH systems, ordering, and taking inventory<br>
-Experience with restaurant opening and closing procedures <br>
-Must be able to handle stressful situations with ease and assertiveness<br>
-Ability to effectively lead others<br>
-A fantastic attitude and strong passion for quality<br>
<br>
Respond with your resume or visit the restaurant Monday-Friday 2-4pm to apply.<br>
<br>
***Acanto is an Equal Opportunity Employer    </section>

